refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
boolctype_punct stringtext
Gibt &true; zurück, wenn alle Zeichen in text durckbar sind, aber weder Buchstaben, Ziffern oder Leerzeichen. Anderenfalls wird &false; zurückgegeben.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns &true; if every character in text 
 is printable, but neither letter, digit or blank, &false; otherwise.

  &reftitle.examples;



    A ctype_punct example


<?php
$strings = array('ABasdk!@!$#', '!@ # $', '*&$()');
foreach ($strings as $testcase) {
    if (ctype_punct($testcase)) {
        echo "The string $testcase consists of all punctuation.\n";
    } else {
        echo "The string $testcase does not consist of all punctuation.\n";
    }
}
?>


    &example.outputs;


The string ABasdk!@!$# does not consist of all punctuation.
The string !@ # $ does not consist of all punctuation.
The string *&$() consists of all punctuation.
